  "sections": {
    "Background": {
      "text": "Caused by one of three methods:\nHematogenous spread (33%)\nContiguous infection from middle ear, sinus, teeth (33%)\nDirect implantation by surgery or penetrating trauma (10%)\nMicrobiology\nStreptococci\nin 50% of cases\n[1]\nAnaerobes\nand\nGram-negative\nrods are typical pathogens\nStaph\nis involved with direct implantation cases",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
