    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Patients rarely appear acutely ill\nClassic triad of headache, fever,\nAND\nfocal neuro deficit is present in <33%\nHeadache\nis most common symptom (present in almost all cases)\nFever\n(~50% of patients)\nFocal neuro\nsymptoms or seizure (~33% of patients)\nNeck stiffness (<50% of patients)\nSigns of\nincreased ICP\n:\npapilledema\n,\nvomiting\n,\nconfusion\n,\nobtundation\n(50% of patients)",
